&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ease of Use&lt;/strong&gt;: The tool should be user-friendly and integrate seamlessly with your existing systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cost&lt;/strong&gt;: Consider your budget. Some tools offer free trials, while others have monthly subscriptions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;: Look for AI agents that provide the functionalities you need without unnecessary extras.&lt;/li&gt;
